Moves - Toxic

Categories: Ailment

A move that leaves the target badly poisoned. Its poison damage worsens every turn.

Stats

TypePoison
Classstatus class
Power–
Accuracy90
PP10
TargetSelected Pokémon
PriorityNormal

Special Effects

  • Inflicts Poison on the target(s).
  • Lasts 15 turns.

Flags

  • Blocked by Detect and Protect

    This move will not work if the target has used Detect or Protect this turn.

  • Reflectable

    This move may be reflected back at the user with Magic Coat or Magic Bounce.

  • Copied by Mirror Move

    A Pokémon targeted by this move can use Mirror Move to copy it.

Description

Badly poisons the target. Never misses when used by a Poison-type Pokémon.
